Checklist for the time when a new version is about to be released:

1.  check spelling.
2.  check examples.
3.  check documentation on Random* and GraphAttributeStatistics.
4.  check version number
5.  check release date.
6.  build the manual.
7.  clean up backup files.
8.  commit changes.
9.  push to git repository.
10. push to webpage
    --> git pull, main-master.zip, cheatsheet.pdf, manual.pdf, online manual.
11. update webpage
12. alert on yagsnews@xamanek.izt.uam.mx